'''三茂钪'''是一种{{le|有机钪化合物|Organoscandium chemistry}}，化学式为Sc(C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它是稻草色的晶体，可由无水[[三氯化钪|三氯化钪]]和[[环戊二烯基钠|环戊二烯基钠]]在[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]中反应得到。<ref name=Wil />若以[[三氟化钪|三氟化钪]]和[[二茂镁|二茂镁]]为原料反应，则会得到三茂钪和氟化二茂钪的混合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Organometallic Chemistry|volume=291|issue=1|language=en|date=1985-08|pages=35–41|doi=10.1016/0022-328X(85)80200-X|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022328X8580200X|title=The reaction of scandium trifluoride with cyclopentadienyl salts and the crystal and molecular structure of the trimer of fluorodicyclopentadienylscandium|accessdate=2020-12-09|author=Frank Bottomley, Daniel E. Paez, Peter S. White|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627004301/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022328X8580200X|dead-url=no}}</ref>它遇水分解，生成[[环戊二烯|环戊二烯]]和[[氢氧化钪|氢氧化钪]]。<ref name=Wil>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=76|issue=23|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1954-12|pages=6210–6210|doi=10.1021/ja01652a114|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01652a114|title=CYCLOPENTADIENYL COMPOUNDS OF Sc, Y, La, Ce AND SOME LANTHANIDE ELEMENTS|accessdate=2020-12-09|author=G. Wilkinson, J. M. Birmingham|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716085835/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01652a114|dead-url=no}}</ref>

